values.value: On this page, you will be able to view the list of 2022 host organizations and projects and choose your preferred host placements. We encourage you to be flexible when selecting your preferred placements, as flexibility may improve your chances of being matched with a host organization.
Candidates who submit their preferences by 11:59pm PT on February 13th will be considered for the first round of matching decisions.
